-union-of-india-chief-justice-4652584%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20Didn't%20Retain%20Sovereignty%20When%20It%20Joined%20Union%20Of%20India%3A%20Chief%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20told%20to%20conduct%20an%20Assembly%20election%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20completed%20five%20years%20under%20control%20of%20the%20central%20government%20-%20the%20second-longest%20period%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20the%20country%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702279680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fc5p4n3lg_supreme-court-premises_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-hearing-not-every-centres-decision-can-be-challenged-says-chief-justice-4652637%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20refused%20to%20rule%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20-%20imposed%20in%20December%202018%20-%20since%20it%20had%20not%20been%20specifically%20challenged%20by%20petitioners%20arguing%20against%20the%20scrapping%20of%20special%20status%2C%20under%20Article%20356.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-hearing-not-every-centres-decision-can-be-challenged-says-chief-justice-4652637%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-hearing-not-every-centres-decision-can-be-challenged-says-chief-justice-4652637%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-hearing-not-every-centres-decision-can-be-challenged-says-chief-justice-4652637%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Historic%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%20Ruling%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Sets%20Election%20Deadline%22%2C%22c