ved%20176%20bags%20and%20140%20of%20them%20have%20been%20counted%2C%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20counted%20today.%20Officials%20from%203%20banks%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20counting%20process%2C%20and%2050%20of%20our%20officials%20are%20involved.%20About%2040%20(currency%20counting)%20machines%20were%20brought%20here%2C%2025%20are%20in%20use%20and%2015%20are%20kept%20as%20backup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20continued%20its%20raid%20on%20Boudh%20Distilleries%20Private%20Limited%2C%20expanding%20its%20scope%20to%20include%20Baldev%20Sahu%20Infra%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20a%20company%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Sahu's%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20suspects%20that%20the%20massive%20cache%20of%20cash%20unearthed%20during%20raids%20on%20Boudh%20Distilleries%20and%20associated%20entities%20represents%20unaccounted%20income%20generated%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20country%20liquor.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Steps%20Up%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20launched%20a%20powerful%20counter-offensive%20on%20Sunday%2C%20aiming%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20declared%20that%20their%20prior%20accusations%20of%20the%20government%20misusing%20investigative%20agencies%20are%20now%20exposed%20as%20mere%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%2C%26quot%3B%20driven%20by%20their%20fear%20of%20being%20held%20accountable%20for%20their%20alleged%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Mr%20Sahu%2C%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20questioned%20why%20no%20searches%20were%20conducted%20against%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20assured%20the%20public%20that%20%26quot%3Blooted%20money%26quot%3B%20would%20be