is%20aimed%20at%20limiting%20the%20oil%20earnings%20that%20would%20go%20to%20Russia's%20war%20chest%20while%20still%20keeping%20the%20global%20oil%20trade%20flowing.%20The%20restrictions%20also%20prohibit%20insurance%20and%20shipping%20services%20for%20vessels%20carrying%20oil%20sold%20above%20the%20price%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Russia%20still%20managed%20to%20sell%2099%25%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussia-oil-sanctions-g7-price-cap-war-ukraine-putin-moscow-economy-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOctober%20oil%20exports%20%3C%2Fa%3Eabove%20the%20%2460%20a%20barrel%20price%20cap%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20report%20and%20KSE%20Institute%20research.%C2%A0During%20the%20month%20of%20October%2C%20oil%20exported%20from%20the%20major%20ports%20of%20Russia%20sold%20for%20an%20average%20of%20%2479.40%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20oil%20exports%20have%20been%20boosted%20by%20a%20shadow%20fleet%20of%20ships%20carrying%20the%20commodity.%20These%20are%20vessels%20that%20do%20not%20have%20adequate%20insurance%2C%20have%20switched%20off%20their%20tracking%20systems%2C%20or%20are%20deliberately%20hiding%20their%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDark%20fleets%20transported%20about%2045%25%20of%20Russia's%20oil%20exports%20this%20year%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20also%20managed%20to%20circumvent%20sanctions%20by%20pivoting%20from%20its%20previous%20major%20market%20in%20Europe%20to%20alternative%20markets%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fchina-india-russian-oil-crude-moscow-war-ukraine-volumes-kpler-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20Russia's%20energy%20sales%2C%20the%20country's%20economy%20has%20remained%20seemingly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-war-economy-go