s%20there%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20supply%20of%20her%20blood%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20relative%20of%20Yu%2C%20an%20aunt%20on%20her%20father's%20side%20of%20the%20family%2C%20called%20the%20Shanghai%20Municipal%20Health%20Commission%20for%20assistance%2C%20and%20the%20organization%20put%20together%20a%20team%20of%20doctors%20who%20coordinated%20blood%20donations%20to%20stabilize%20her%20condition%2C%20per%20The%20Paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2016%2C%20several%20dozen%20local%20civil%20servants%2C%20including%20police%20officers%20and%20firefighters%2C%20donated%20blood%20to%20Yu%2C%20whose%20life%20was%20eventually%20saved%2C%20The%20Paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paper%20wrote%20that%20these%20individuals%20had%20volunteered%2C%20and%20that%20some%20even%20put%20out%20a%20social%20media%20call%20among%20their%20colleagues%20for%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWeibo%20is%20not%20buying%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20people%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20Twitter%2C%20were%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20began%20questioning%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20donations%20after%20Yu%20released%20a%20video%20on%20Douyin%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20TikTok%2C%20sharing%20the%20events%20that%20occurred.%20Her%20video%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20she%20posted%20several%20screenshots%20of%20texts%20with%20her%20husband%20discussing%20the%20organization%20of%20the%20blood%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Ngari%20region's%20type%20A%20blood%20has%20been%20transfused%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu's%20husband%20wrote%20in%20the%20screenshot%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%20more%20than%207%2C000%20milliliters%2C%20your%20entire%20body's%20worth%20of%20blood%20was%20replaced%20twice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20thus%20went%20viral%20in%20late%20November%20under%20the%20moniker%20%26quot%3BBlood%20Tank%20Sister%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BH