%20of%20violations%20done%20by%20the%20state%20and%20its%20actors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20emphasised%20the%20original%20intent%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20stating%20its%20aim%20was%20to%20gradually%20integrate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purpose%20of%20Article%20370%20was%20to%20slowly%20bring%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20par%20with%20the%20other%20states%20of%20India.%20The%20requirement%20of%20recommendation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Constituent%20Assembly%20cannot%20be%20read%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20makes%20the%20larger%20intention%20redundant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20acknowledging%20the%20need%20for%20gradual%20integration%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20use%20of%20%26quot%3Bbackdoor%20amendments%26quot%3B%20to%20bypass%20established%20procedures.%20He%20stressed%20that%20when%20a%20specific%20method%20for%20amendment%20is%20prescribed%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20outlined%20in%20Article%20367%2C%20it%20must%20be%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegarding%20the%20amendment%20of%20Article%20370%20using%20367%2C%20I%20have%20said%20when%20a%20procedure%20is%20prescribed%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20followed.%20Amendment%20through%20the%20backdoor%20not%20permissible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20validated%20the%20government's%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%2C%20a%20constitutional%20provision%20that%20bestowed%20special%20status%20upon%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20facilitate%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20within%20a%20specific%20timeframe%2C%20setting%20the%20deadline%20for%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2