0of%20power%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20valid%20and%20not%20malafide.%20And%20that%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20power%20to%20notify%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20subsists%20even%20after%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20parliament%20can%20convert%20a%20state%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory%20is%20left%20open%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20doing%20so%20because%20the%20solicitor%20general%20has%20promised%20that%20statehood%20will%20be%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20added%20that%20not%20every%20decision%20by%20the%20Centre%20can%20be%20challenged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20bench%20comprises%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20along%20with%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Surya%20Kant.%20This%20bench%20had%20reserved%20judgment%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-jammu-and-kashmir-all-eyes-are-on-the-supreme-court-today%5C%22%3E%20in%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20heard%20for%2016%20days%2C%20on%20September%205.%20There%20was%20a%20three-year%20gap%20in%20the%20matter%E2%80%99s%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20pronounced%20three%20judgments.%20One%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20for%20himself%20and%20Justices%20Gavai%20and%20Surya%20Kant.%20A%20concurring%20opinion%20was%20authored%20by%20Justice%20Kaul%20and%20Justice%20Khanna%20concurred%20with%20both%2C%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20petitions%20had%20challenged%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Farticle-370-understanding-the-history-legal-contexts-and-why-it-matters%5C%22%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20brought%20unilaterally%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%2C%20while%20reading%20out%20the%20judgment%20said%20the%20issues%20at%20hand%20were%3A%20whether%20Article%20370%20is%20temporary%2C%20whether%20substitution%20of%20%E2%80%98constituent%20assembly%E2%80%99%20by%20legislative%20assembly%20by%20using%20370(1)(d)%20is%20valid%2C%20and%20also%20whether%20the%20Presidential%20Order%20is%20invalid%20for%20lack%20of%20recommendation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constituent%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20considered%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20Presidential%20Rule%20imposed%20in%20December%202018%20and%20its%20subsequent%20extensions%20are%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20the%20court%20considered%20whether%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20Act%20is%20constitutionally%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20bringing%20this%20legislation%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20put%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20mainstream%20politicians%20and%20others%20in%20prolonged%20house%20arrest%2C%20and%20brought%20in%20what%20was%20then%20the%20longest%20period%20of%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20a%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbrought%20an%20unprecedented%20development%2C%20progress%2C%20security%2C%20and%20stability%20to%20the%20region%2C%20which%20was%20often%20missing%20during%20the%20old%20Article%20370%20regime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20tweeted%20their%20reactions%20after%20the%20verdict%20were%20Kapil%20Sibal%20and%20National%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20Omar%20Abdullah.%20The%20latter%20had%20been%20in%20house%20arrest%20for%20months%20after%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECourts%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20battles%20are%20fought%20to%20be%20lost%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20history%20must%20record%20the%20uncomfortable%20facts%20for%20generations%20to%20know%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20and%20wrong%