E2%80%9Cnever%20had%20any%20intention%20of%20creating%20hurdles%20in%20a%20caste-based%20survey%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20Shah%2C%20while%20chairing%20the%2026th%20meeting%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Zonal%20Council%20at%20Patna%2C%20said%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20had%20supported%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20caste-based%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20claimed%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20were%20some%20issues%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20central%20government%20never%20had%20any%20intention%20of%20creating%20hurdles%20in%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%20When%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Bihar%2C%20it%20supported%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%20The%20governor%20also%20approved%20the%20bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20August%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-govt-defensive-over-bihar-caste-survey-changes-affidavit-in-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ehad%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%2C%20controversially%2C%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20it%20changed%20the%20paragraph%20in%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%2C%20claiming%20this%20one%20line%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinadvertently%20crept%20in%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20held%20that%20the%20Census%20Act%20of%201948%20empowers%20only%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20conduct%20the%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20had%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20against%20a%20Caste%20Census%20nationally%20at%20this%20point.%20Bihar%20eventually%20finished%20the%20state%20caste%20survey%2C%20and%20tabled%20the%20report%20in%20the%20assembly.%20Similar%20surveys%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20comments%20may%20be%20construed%20as%20defensive%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20stance%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sole%20authority%20which%20can%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702274140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170436%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.04.26-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Funion-govt-never-intended-to-create-hurdles-in-caste-based-survey-amit-shah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20home%20minister's%20comments%20may%20be%20construed%20as%20defensive%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20government's%20earlier%20stance%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sole%20authority%20which%20can%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Funion-govt-never-intended-to-create-hurdles-in-caste-based-survey-amit-shah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Why%20Smriti%20has%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20'notebook'%20of%20Shreyanka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702274008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105893377%2Cimgsize-92418.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-why-smriti-mandhana-has-a-mention-in-the-notebook-of-shreyanka-patil%2Farticleshow%2F105893465.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20women's%20cricket%20team%20secure%20a%20five-wicket%20victory%20against%20England%20in%20the%20final%20Women's%20T20%20International%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%20India's%20rookie%20spinners%2C%20Shreyanka%20Patil%20(3-19)%20and%20Saika%20Ishaque%20(3-22)%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20bowling%20out%20England%20for%20126.%20Smriti%20Mandhana%20(48)%20and%20Jemimah%20Rodrigues%20(29)%20contribute%20to%20India's%20successful%20chase.%20Amanjot%20Kaur's%20unbeaten%2013%20runs%20help%20seal%20the%20win.%20The%20victory%20marks%20India's%20first%20home%20win%20against%20England%20since%20March%202018%2C%20providing%20momentum%20for%20the%20upcoming%20one-off%20Test%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-why-smriti-mandhana-has-a-mention-in-the-notebook-of-shreyanka-patil%2Farticleshow%2F105893465.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Removing%20Special%20Status%20Of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constitutionally%20Valid%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESupreme%20Court%20upholds%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20scrapping%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-verdict-live-updates-supreme-court-verdict-on-validity-of-scrapping-article-370-in-jammu-and-kashmir-today-4652207%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20cannot%20sit%20in%20appeal%20over%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India%20on%20whether%20the%20special%20circumstances%20under%20Article%20370%20exist.%20History%20shows%20the%20gradual%20process%20of%20constitutional%20integration%20was%20not%20going%20on.%20It%20was%20not%20as%20if%20after%2070%20years%2C%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20was%20applied%20in%20one%20go.%20It%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20the%20integration%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20direct%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20shall%20be%20done%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20direct%20that%20steps%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20Election%20commission%20to%20conduct%20elections%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20held%20that%20all%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20using%20Article%20370(1)(d)%20in%20one%20go.%20We%20do%20not%20find%20the%20use%20of%20Presidential%20power%20to%20issue%20CO%20273%20was%20mala%20fide.%20Thus%20we%20hold%20the%20exercise%20of%20Presidential%20power%20to%20be%20valid.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20principle%20of%20consultation%20and%20collaboration%20was%20not%20required%20to%20be%20followed%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20Presidential%20power.%20Concurrence%20of%20the%20state%20government%20was%20not%20required%20to%20apply%20all%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20using%20Article%20370(1)(d).%20So%20the%20President%20taking%20the%20concurrence%20of%20the%20Union%20Govt%20was%20not%20mala%20fide.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20held%20that%20Article%20370%20is%20a%20temporary%20provision.%20Article%20370%20was%20an%20interim%20arrangement%20due%20to%20war%20conditions%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20does%20not%20have%20internal%20sovereignty%20different%20from%20other%20states.%20Whether%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20retained%20an%20element%20of%20sovereignty%20or%20internal%20sovereignty%20when%20it%20joined%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20we%20have%20held%20no.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20a%20clear%20absence%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20the%20reference%20of%20sovereignty.%20That%20the%20State%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20became%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20is%20evident%20from%20Articles%201%20and%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20refuses%20to%20rule%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20Presidential%20rule%20imposed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20December%202018%20since%20it%20was%20not%20specifically%20challenged%20by%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20a%20proclamation%20under%20Article%20356%20comes%20into%20force%2C%20countless%20decisions%20are%20taken%20by%20the%20Centre.%20Not%20every%20action%20can%20be%20challenged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702273980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fmemaljuo_supreme-court-article-370-_625x300_11_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-didnt-retain-sovereignty-when-it-joined-union-of-india-chief-justice-4652584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20delivered%20its%20verdict%20on%20a%20highly%20anticipated%20case%20with%20far-reaching%20consequences%3A%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20Centre's%202019%20decision%20to%20revoke%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-didnt-retain-sovereignty-when-it-joined-union-of-india-chief-justice-4652584%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-didnt-retain-sovereignty-when-it-joined-union-of-india-chief-justice-4652584%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-didnt-retain-sovereignty-when-it-joined-union-of-india-chief-justice-4652584%2Famp%2F1%2