-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E's%20performance%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20was%20a%20major%20reason%20behind%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20smooth%20sailing%20till%20the%20final.%20The%20fast%20bowler%20missed%20the%20first%20few%20matches%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20from%20finishing%20as%20the%20top%20wicket-taker%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20who%20finished%20on%20top%20of%20the%20bowling%20charts%20with%2024%20wickets%20from%20seven%20matches%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20has%20been%20India's%20go-to%20bowler%20in%20ODIs%20and%20Tests.%20His%20popularity%20has%20surged%20after%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Shami%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20growing%20up%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20then%20played%20national-level%20cricket%20for%20Bengal%20before%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20Mohammed%20Shami%20recently%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20hobbies%20and%20his%20growing%20up%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20travelling%2C%20fishing.%20I%20like%20driving%20a%20lot.%20I%20like%20driving%20bike%20and%20cars.%20But%20after%20playing%20for%20India%2C%20I%20have%20stopped%20driving%20bikes.%20What%20if%20I%20get%20injured%3F%20I%20drive%20bike%20on%20highways%2C%20may%20be%20sometimes%20in%20village%20when%20I%20go%20to%20meet%20my%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20said%20on%20PUMA's%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EZameen%20se%20hi%20aaya%20hu.%20Kheto%20ki%20jo%20booghi%20hoti%20hai%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20have%20driven%20tractor%2C%20bus%2C%20trucks.%20I%20have%20driven%20bus%20in%20truck.%20One%20of%20my%20school%20friends%20had%20a%20truck%20in%20his%20house.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20drive.%20I%20was%20small%20then%20and%20was%20driving%20on%20a%20ground.%20I%20drove%20our%20tractor%20into%20the%20pond%20too.%20My%20father%20scolded%20me.%2