20Descalsota%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChicken%20rice%20is%20Singapore's%20best-known%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETian%20Tian's%20version%20has%20earned%20the%20praise%20of%20Gordon%20Ramsay%2C%20Anthony%20Bourdain%2C%20and%20the%20Michelin%20Guide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20certainly%20lives%20up%20to%20the%20hype%20and%20is%20well%20worth%20the%20slightly%20higher%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHawker%20centers%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0or%20open-air%20food%20courts%20%E2%80%94%20are%20the%20core%20of%20Singapore's%20vibrant%20food%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Singapore%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20have%20been%20eating%20at%20hawker%20centers%20ever%20since.%20These%20casual%20dining%20spots%20found%20across%20the%20island%20offer%20delicious%2C%20inexpensive%20meals%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20Food%20Centre%2C%20located%20in%20Singapore's%20vibrant%20Chinatown%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20It%20was%20opened%20in%201928%20and%20survived%20World%20War%20II%20and%20the%20Japanese%20occupation.%20Back%20then%2C%20dishes%20were%20served%20for%20as%20little%20as%20eight%20Singapore%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20taken%20during%20Maxwell's%20early%20days%20show%20locals%20sitting%20on%20simple%20stools%20around%20circular%20tables.%20People%20can%20be%20seen%20lining%20up%20outside%20dozens%20of%20food%20carts.%20The%20ceilings%20were%20covered%20with%20metal%20scaffolding%2C%20and%20overhead%20fans%20hung%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20space%20isn't%20all%20that%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20only%20eaten%20at%20Maxwell%20a%20handful%20of%20times%2C%20as%20I%20live%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20city%2C%20just%2010%20minutes%20away%20from%20another%20popular%20hawker%20center%20in%20eastern%20Singapore%2C%20and%20usually%20frequent%20that%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20Maxwell%20Food%20Center%20in%20November%2C%20I%20was%20greeted%20by%20a%20similar%20scene%20to%20the%20photos%20from%20its%20past%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20major%20differences%20were%20the%20renovated%2C%20enclosed%20stalls%20and%20the%20hanging%20lamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20are%20over%20100%20stalls%20at%20Maxwell%20Food%20Centre%2C%20but%20one%20stands%20out.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20hawker%20stall%20selling%20chicken%20rice%20in%20singapore%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65558b624ca513d8242a59ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETian%20Tian%20Hainanese%20Chicken%20Rice%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20stalls%20at%20Maxwell%20Food%20Centre.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETian%20Tian%20Hainanese%20Chicken%20Rice%20is%20an%20icon%20among%20Singapore%20hawkers.%20The%20stall's%20popularity%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20regularly%20spotted%20snaking%20line%20of%20diners%20who%20often%20wait%20up%20to%20an%20hour%20for%20a%20plate%20of%20chicken%20rice.%20It's%20Singapore's%20unofficial%20national%20dish%2C%20and%20made%20up%20of%20poached%20or%20roasted%20chicken%2C%20steamed%20white%20rice%2C%20and%20sambal%2C%20a%20local%20chili%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20at%20Tian%20Tian%20for%20lunch%2C%20about%2015%20people%20were%20waiting%20in%20line.%20The%20atmosphere%20was%20buzzing.%20Tourists%20chatted%20excitedly%20about%20which%20dishes%20they%20were%20curious%20to%20try%2C%20with%20one%20noting%20that%20the%20fragrance%20of%20the%20chicken%20was%20making%20their%20mouth%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETian%20Tian%20has%20appeared%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-the-michelin-list-ruined-hawker-culture-food-for-singapore-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichelin%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202016%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20few%20stalls%20listed%20in%20the%20coveted%20Bib%20Gourmand%20%E2%80%94%20a%20list%20of%20the%20best%20establishments%20serving%20dishes%20%26quot%3Bat%20an%20affordable%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20believes%20in%20Tian%20Tian's%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNice%20meh%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20middle-aged%20man%20asked%20me%20in%20Singlish%2C%20the%20creole%20of%20Singapore%2C%20upon%20seeing%20my%20drop-off%20location.%20The%20man%20had%20just%20picked%20me%20up%20on%20a%20ride-hailing%20service%20and%20was%20ferrying%20me%20to%20Maxwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20places%20in%20Bedok%20and%20Tampines%20serve%20better%20chicken%20rice.%20It's%20a%20tourist%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20referring%20to%20residential%20areas%20in%20eastern%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20were%20also%20locals%20who%20praised%20the%20stalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20in%20line%2C%20I%20met%20another%20local%2C%20Bennett%20Lee.%20Lee%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20his%2050s%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20casual%20T-shirt%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20shorts%2C%20and%20he%20told%20me%20he%20was%20running%20errands%20and%20decided%20to%20drop%20by%20for%20lunch%20%E2%80%94%20a%20routine%20he%20follows%20a%20few%20times%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20proclaimed%20the%20stall%20served%20one%20of%20the%20best%20chicken%20rice%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSingaporeans%20are%20spoiled%20for%20choice.%20And%20we%20know%20good%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20nice%2C%20especially%20the%20steamed%20chicken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ordered%20the%20roasted%20chicken%20set%20and%20a%20side%20of%20vegetables%20for%2010%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20%247.50.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225446%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20plate%20of%20chicken%20rice%20and%20veggies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%