world%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20It'll%20also%20be%20expanding%20the%20McCrispy%20into%20tenders%20and%20wraps.%20It%20cut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-chicken-wraps-return-menu-due-to-chicken-demand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echicken%20snack%20wraps%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20its%20menus%20years%20ago%20because%20employees%20and%20franchises%20said%20they%20were%20too%20complicated%20to%20make.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20Spicy%20Deluxe%20McCrispy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65761fda7a3c8094d5db7781%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcDonald's%20plans%20to%20bring%20the%20McCrispy%20to%20all%20its%20markets%20by%202025.%20%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20said%20it%20will%20also%20improve%20a%20classic%20menu%20item%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20its%20burger%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20new%20Best%20Burger%20initiative%20that%20it'll%20deploy%20into%20almost%20all%20its%20markets%20by%202026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20comes%20after%20years%20of%20testing%20the%20right%20strategy%20to%20make%20the%20McDonald's%20burger%20as%20delicious%20as%20possible%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhospitality%2Fmcdonalds-burger-new-menu-2400d22b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20found%20that%20one%20of%20the%20keys%20to%20taste%20is%20cooking%20fewer%20burgers%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20it%20has%20also%20calculated%20just%20how%20much%20to%20press%20down%20on%20its%20burgers%20(to%20the%20millimeter)%20with%20the%20metal%20clamp%20used%20to%20cook%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%20Other%20changes%20it'll%20make%20will%20be%20slicing%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20the%20brioche%20bun%20thicker%20to%20preserve%20heat%2C%20cooking%20the%20onions%20on%20top%20of%20the%20beef%20patty%2C%20and%20taking%20the%20cheese%20out%20of%20the%20refrigerator%20ahead%20of%20time%20so%20it%20will%20melt%20faster%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20McDonald's%20first%20tested%20the%20strategy%20in%20Australia%20and%20saw%20positive%20results%2C%20it%20began%20piloting%20the%20approach%20in%20its%20West%20Coast%20restaurants%20and%20Midwest%20locations%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%20The%20company%20plans%20to%20deploy%20the%20program%20in%20all%20its%20US%20locations%20by%202024%2C%20the%20Journal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20also%20said%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-to-start-selling-bigger-burgers-menu-fast-food-restaurants-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eplans%20to%20sell%20bigger%20burgers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20investor%20update%20last%20week%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20that's%20linked%20to%20the%20Best%20Burger%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CosMc's%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570f7ac58e7c0c29a2a786c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECosMc's%20food%20include%20pretzel%20bites%20and%20cookies%20and%20specialty%20drinks.%20%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20also%20revealed%20a%20few%20more%20details%2C%20including%20menu%20items%2C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-compete-starbucks-drink-focused-cosmcs-launch-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECosMc's%2C%20its%20new%20restaurant%20concept%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20aims%20to%20solve%20the%20%26quot%3B3pm%20slump%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20might%20give%20Starbucks%20a%20run%20for%20its%20