iberation%2C%20and%20after%20appointment%20of%20three%20observers%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20finally%20named%20former%20Union%20minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20their%20chief%20minister%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Senior%20tribal%20leader%20and%20a%20crowd%20favourite%2C%20the%20Kunkuri%20MLA%20is%20a%20four-time%20MP%20and%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20Jashpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201964%20in%20Jashpur%20district%E2%80%99s%20Bagia%20village%2C%20Sai%20started%20his%20political%20career%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201989.%20Hailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20politicians%2C%20Sai%20is%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20His%20uncle%20Narhari%20Prasad%20Sai%20served%20as%20a%20two%20time%20MLA%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20was%20a%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Janata%20Party%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20too%20became%20a%20central%20government%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%202014%20Modi%20government%20and%20was%20entrusted%20with%20portfolios%20like%20steel%2C%20mining%20and%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20BJP%20lost%20Chhattisgarh%20in%202018%2C%20Sai%20was%20made%20the%20BJP%20state%20chief.%20On%20the%20international%20day%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20indigenous%20people%20last%20year%2C%20Sai%20was%20sacked%20from%20the%20post%20earning%20BJP%20heavy%20criticism.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20Arun%20Sao%2C%20an%20OBC%20face%20brought%20forward%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20counter%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20OBC-politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20Kanwar%20tribe%2C%20Sai%20had%20declared%20property%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%20crore%20in%20the%20just%20concluded%20state%20election.%20Within%20the%20party%2C%20he%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20disciplined%20BJP%20leader%20and%20a%20Sangh%20loyalist.%20His%20name%20had%20been%20in%20the%20running%20since%20BJP%20won%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20results%20declared%20on%20December%203%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2054%20out%20of%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%2017%20of%20the%2029%20tribal%20seats.%20After%20the%20tough%20line%20followed%20by%20Congress%20on%20the%20OBC%20card%2C%20many%20within%20the%20BJP%20thought%20that%20the%20the%20party%20would%20follow%20suit%20and%20name%20an%20OBC%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20experts%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20played%20the%20tribal%20card%20as%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20political%20narrative%20the%20it%20is%20building%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20has%20a%20tribal%20president%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20known%20to%20be%20rife%20with%20tribal%20issues.%20It%20makes%20complete%20sense%20to%20put%20a%20tribal%20CM%20in%20the%20state.%20Especially%2C%20from%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20over%20the%20years%20felt%20neglected%20in%20the%20larger%20political%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20analyst%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20who%20was%20encouraged%20by%20Dilip%20Singh%20Judev%20to%20join%20politics%2C%20had%20managed%20to%20be%20close%20to%20former%20Chattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Raman%20Singh%20as%20well.%20In%20a%20fractured%20party%2C%20Sai%20had%20managed%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20good%20books%20of%20most%20leaders.%20This%2C%20many%20believe%2C%20will%20come%20in%20handy%20for%20him%20in%20handling%20the%20various%20factions%20simmering%20within%20the%20majority%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20appointment%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20setting%20the%20narrative%20for%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20leaders%20for%20Chhattisgarh.%20Within%20this%20new%20crop%2C%20the%20party%20seems%20to%20be%20instilling%20a%20kind%20of%20discipline%2C%20a%20perceived%20sense%20that%20positions%20of%20power%20come%20to%20those%20who%20wait%20diligently%20and%20work%20silently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Sai%20is%20a%20tribal%20face%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20has%20always%20put%20the%20party%20before%20his%20identity.%20In%20fact%2C%20tribal%20leaders%20believe%20that%20since%20he%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20political%20career%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20he%20has%20a%20certain%20disconnect%20from%20the%20tribal%20issues%20of%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20announced%20Vijay%20Sharma%20and%20Arun%20Sao%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20and%20Raman%20Singh%20as%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20while%20the%20suspense%20over%20who%20will%20bag%20the%20posts%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20continues.%20However%2C%20by%20choosing%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20certainly%20hopes%20to%20win%20brownie%20points%20in%20identity%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702216854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Sai's%20appointment%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20setting%20the%20narrative%20for%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20leaders%20for%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smile%20Direct%20Club%20dentistry%20aligners%20firm%20shuts%20down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702216435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2CFD%2Fproduction%2F_131971511_gettyimages-1436969196.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67675431