(intentionally%20insulting%20or%20intimidating%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20Tribe%20and%20abusing%20them%20by%20caste%20name%20in%20public%20view)%3B%203(1)(s)%20(abusing%20any%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20by%20caste%20name%20in%20any%20place%20within%20public%20view)%3B%20and%203(2)%20va%20(committing%20any%20offence%20specified%20in%20the%20Schedule%20against%20a%20person%20or%20property%2C%20knowing%20that%20such%20person%20is%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20or%20such%20property%20belongs%20to%20such%20a%20member%2C%20shall%20be%20punishable%20with%20such%20punishment%20as%20specified%20under%20the%20IPC%20for%20such%20offenses%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20a%20fine.)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702211417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06103243%2FScreenshot-2023-12-06-at-10.30.47-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frajasthan-fir-against-hawa-mahal-mla-balmukunt-acharya-for-alleged-assault-on-sc-community-member%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20with%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20against%20Acharya%20for%20violating%20street%20vendor%20laws%20when%20instructing%20Muslim%20vendors%20to%20close%20their%20shops%20in%20the%20Hawa%20Mahal%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frajasthan-fir-against-hawa-mahal-mla-balmukunt-acharya-for-alleged-assault-on-sc-community-member%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tallinn-Winning%20Erect%20Penis%20Comedy%20%E2%80%98Tentigo%E2%80%99%20Set%20for%20Indian%20Remake%20%E2%80%93%20SGIFF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702211400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FTentigo.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D56