%3E%3Cspan%3ESharif%2C%20who%20leads%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20%E2%80%93%20Nawaz%20(PML-N)%2C%20was%20speaking%20to%20aspirants%20for%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20tickets%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20delivered%20all%20three%20times%20that%20he%20served%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20and%20yet%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20he%20was%20sent%20packing%20from%20the%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20tenure%20as%20PM.%20Two%20Indian%20prime%20ministers%20visited%20Pakistan.%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Esaab%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20(Atal)%20Vajpayee%20%3Cem%3Esaab%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20come%20to%20Lahore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20quoted%20Sharif%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20have%20to%20improve%20our%20relations%20with%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iran.%20We%20need%20to%20make%20more%20strong%20relations%20with%20China%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegretting%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20poor%20economy%2C%20he%20attacked%20the%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20supremo%20Imran%20Khan%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20economy%20witnessed%20a%20downfall%20during%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20government%20(2008-2022).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-news-nawaz-sharif-wanted-better-relations-with-india-was-ousted-for-opposing-kargil-101702116041011.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sharif%20also%20restated%20his%20call%20for%20demanding%20accountability%20of%20former%20military%20generals%20and%20judges%20for%20ruining%20Pakistan%20by%20overthrowing%20his%20government%20in%202017%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20brought%20this%20country%20to%20this%20level%20should%20be%20made%20accountable%20as%20patriotic%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20to%20their%20country.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20come%20into%20power%20to%20roam%20around%20in%20luxury%20cars%20but%20we%20want%20accountability%20of%20those%20(who)%20ruined%20this%20country%20and%20made%20false%20cases%20against%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202006%2C%20General%20Musharraf%2C%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20Line%20of%20Fire%3A%20A%20Memoir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20had%20referred%20to%20this%20disagreement%20with%20Sharif%20on%20Kargil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fworld%2Fkargil-episode-brought-musharraf-and-sharif-on-collision-course-1188094.html%5C%22%3Estating%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kargil%20episode%20created%20the%20biggest%20divide%20(between%20the%20two).%20We%20had%20both%20wanted%20to%20put%20Kashmir%20firmly%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20radar%20screen%2C%20politically%20as%20well%20as%20militarily%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20when%20%E2%80%9Cexternal%20political%20pressure%20forced%20Sharif%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20he%20broke%20down.%20%E2%80%9CRather%20than%20deriving%20strength%20through%20national%20solidarity%2C%20he%20(Sharif)%20blamed%20the%20Army%20and%20tried%20to%20make%20himself%20look%20clean.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702209600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23082949%2FF8-FnIeaUAEdglY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fformer-pak-pm-nawaz-sharif-says-he-was-ousted-for-opposing-the-kargil-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharif%20said%20he%20was%20thrown%20out%20by%20General%20Musharraf%2C%20who%20then%20led%20Pakistan's%20army%2C%20because%20he%20suggested%20keeping%20good%20relations%20with%20India%20and%20other%20key%20neighbours.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en