20the%20input%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20even%20established%20a%20water%20bank%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFish%20farming%20did%20not%20prove%20profitable%20for%20us%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20input%20costs.%20If%20we%20sold%20a%20fish%20for%20Rs%20100%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2080.%20We%20were%20only%20left%20with%20Rs%2020%20profit.%20It%20was%20very%20little%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sanjay%20came%20across%20a%20news%20report%20that%20mentioned%20the%20profitability%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming.%20Motivated%20to%20try%20his%20hands%20in%20cultivating%20oysters%2C%20he%20bought%2025%2C000%20oysters%20to%20cultivate%20in%20his%20water%20bank.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20roped%20in%20other%20farmer%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20collective%20investment%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20the%20group%20started%20oyster%20farming.%20And%20in%20a%20year%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89574%2Fsanjay-gandate-pearl-farmer-gadchiroli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerate%20an%20income%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334674%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20their%20success%2C%20about%2040%20farmers%20have%20joined%20Sanjay%20and%20his%20cooperative%20%E2%80%98Bless%20All%20Pearl%20Farmer%20Producer%20Company%E2%80%99.%20Together%2C%20they%20have%20planted%2050%2C000%20oysters%20and%20collaborated%20with%20companies%20like%20GKP%20Pearl%20Farm%20of%20Solapur%20and%20Namo%20Pearl%20Farm%20in%20Chandrapur%20to%20sell%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESix%20tips%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20group%20was%20able%20to%20generate%20a%20handsome%20profit%20in%20their%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20the%20success%20rate%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20was%20not%20as%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20progressive%20farmer%20travelled%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20%E2%80%94%201%2C400%20km%20from%20his%20village%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20formal%20training%20in%20oyster%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F232818%2Fpearl-cultivation-earns-lakhs-urban-garden-cultured-freshwater-pearls-online-classes-business-how-to-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20attended%20a%20seven-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20how%20to%20source%20raw%20material%2C%20how%20to%20nucleate%20oysters%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20pearl%20designs%20that%20are%20in%20demand%2C%20what%20food%20to%20offer%20oysters%2C%20the%20surgical%20procedure%20of%20pearls%2C%20how%20to%20keep%20oysters%20in%20antibiotics%2C%20and%20what%20is%20its%20lifecycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334675%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20pearls%20are%20cultivated%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20source%20good%20quality%20oysters.%20Then%2C%20we%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20The%20oyster%20is%20closed%20and%20is%20kept%20on%20antibiotics%20inside%20a%20smaller%20water%20tank%20for%20two%20to%20three%20days%20and%20then%20shifted%20to%20a%20bigger%20pond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oyster%20then%20secretes%20nacre%20%5Ba%20form%20of%20calcium%20carbonate%5D%20around%20the%20nucleus.%20The%20pearls%20get%20readied%20to%20be%20harvested%20in%2012%20to%2014%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20start%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20for%20beginners%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20identify%20good%20oysters%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20it%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20cultivate%20oysters%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20provided%20you%20cultivate%20good%20quality%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSource%20good%20quality%20oysters%20to%20get%20A-grade%20quality%20pearls.%20The%20size%20of%20the%20oyster%20should%20be%20between%202.5%20to%203%20inches.%20Its%20outer%20cover%20should%20be%20golden%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20the%20market%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98irritants%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20Ganesha%2C%20Rama%2C%20Shiva%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%20(holy%20number%20in%20Islam)%2C%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20pearls%20come%20out%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20these%20symbols%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20Sanjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20be%20informed%20about%20the%20market%20demand.%20If%20you%20implant%20the%20nucleus%20of%20Ganesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20go%20to%20sell%20in%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%20then%20it%20would%20not%20be%20profitable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaster%20the%20easier%20surgery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20there%20are%20several%20types%20of%20surgical%20procedures%20in%20pearl%20cultures%20%E2%80%94%20like%20gonadal%20implantation%2C%20mantle%20tissue%20implantation%2C%20and%20mantle%20cavity%20insertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suggest%20that%20farmers%20learn%20mantle%20tissue%20surgery%20as%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20perform%20and%20the%20chances%20of%20oysters%20are%20higher%20as%20compared%20to%20other%20kinds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20the%20pond%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20informs%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriver-like%20ecosystem%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COysters%20should%20not%20feel%20alienated%20and%20that%20they%20are%20outside%20a%20river.%20They%20must%20have%20a%20river-like%20environment%20to%20thrive.%20To%20ensure%20this%2C%20you%20must%20introduce%20algae%20inside%20the%20pond.%20Algae%20is%20the%20major%20food%20source%20of%20an%20oyster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20pH%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20points%20out%20that%20farmers%20should%20ensure%20a%20pH%20of%20eight%20inside%20the%20water%20tank.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20pH%20is%20more%20than%20eight%20(alkaline)%2C%20oysters%20will%20not%20survive.%20You%20should%20also%20check%20pH%20levels%20weekly.%20If%20the%20pH%20is%20higher%2C%20keep%20changing%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20a%2020%C3%9720%20square%20feet%20pond%20with%2010%20feet%20depth%2C%20it%20would%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20store%20one%20lakh%20litre%20water.%20So%2C%20you%20should%20replace%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20every%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintain%20the%20temperature%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiven%20its%20geography%2C%20Sanjay%20says%20that%20Osmanabad%20has%20a%20fluctuating%20temperature%20between%2020%20and%2040%20degrees%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C