appened%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20taught%20us%20that%20hope%20never%20dies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ujjwala%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700661469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ujjwala%20Sahane%20was%20contemplating%20ending%20her%20life%20when%20her%20daughter%20had%20a%20fall%20that%20left%20her%20deaf%20and%20paralysed.%20A%20Bharatnatyam%20dancer%20today%2C%20this%20is%20her%20story%20of%20hope.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334652%2Fujjwala-sahane-prerana-hearing-impaired-deaf-bharatnatyam-dancer-soul-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctor%20Returned%20From%20The%20US%20To%20Build%20ISO-Certified%20Made-In-India%20Robot%20Making%20Surgeries%20Cheaper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20brief%20encounter%20with%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20Srivastava%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311579%2Fcardiologist-dr-deepak-krishnamurthy-breaks-myth-heart-attack-pain-relief-viral-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20renowned%20cardiologist%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20SS%20Innovations%2C%20experienced%20a%20transformative%20shift%20in%20perspective%20regarding%20his%20work.%20This%20encounter%20took%20place%20during%20a%20fateful%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20which%20ultimately%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20in%20his%20journey%20to%20develop%20made-in-India%20surgical%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20a%2022-year-old%20female%20diagnosed%20with%20an%20atrial%20septal%20defect%20%E2%80%94%20a%20congenital%20heart%20condition%20characterised%20by%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20septum%2C%20the%20wall%20that